data.description: Discover easy living in this charming Sun Terrace villa, featuring two bedrooms and two baths, all on one level. The front unit boasts a built-in entertainment unit and convenient parking right outside. Enjoy the sunny easterly location and a huge screened patio - perfect for relaxation.This villa is ideally located close to everything that the Gardens has to offer, including world-class restaurants, beautiful beaches, and golfing amenities. The Homeowners Association takes care of exterior maintenance, ensuring a hassle-free lifestyle.The property comes equipped with a 2023 air conditioner, newer carpeting, wood grain LVF in living area and sleek white kitchen appliances. Don't miss the opportunity to own this well-maintained and conveniently located villa, offering both comfort and proximity to local attractions.
